    <title>Bug #148 (New): Deactivate Files Module</title>
    <link rel="alternate" href="http://opendesignengine.net/issues/148"/>
    <id>http://opendesignengine.net/issues/148</id>
    <updated>2013-07-18T21:03:28+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Christopher Sigman</name>
    </author>
    <content type="html">
&lt;p&gt;DMSF is a replacement for the files module. As such, the files module should be deactivated.  This can currently be done on a per-project basis, but should be done on a site-wide basis.&lt;/p&gt;    </content>
